entries.femaleVariant: Thanks for the help! Glad you got through to that stubborn mule. Looks like I'm up to bat with him now. Gig closed.
Obviously, I know Max is safe, but... from his state I can tell there were some complications. Ehhh... guess that was to be expected...
I know about Max. I know what happened. Been wondering what to say, what words would hurt the most.
But you know what? Not worth it. I should've known a merc like you wouldn't be up to the task.
I know about Max – that you left him there. This was the one real chance to help, but now… you scared him off. To hide somewhere else.
Corpos will probably track him down before I can. Guess you can work out what that means…
I should've known a merc like you wouldn't be suited for a task this sensitive.
